Interface LogoutEvent

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AdminController, AlbumViewController, LoginController, PhotoViewController, SearchController, SlideshowController, UserViewController

    public interface LogoutEvent
    This interface contains default methods for handling logout and quit events that exist from the MenuBar interaction on every scene.
    Author:
    Derek Schatel

    • Method Summary

      default void logout(javafx.scene.Parent root, AdminList list)
      Handles logout selection from MenuBar.
      default void quit(AdminList list)
      Saves the userlist and then exits the application.
